Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00E3CE42\4c&H00CB8A27}我们的感情互相依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00E3CE42\4c&H00CB8A27}从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00E3CE42\4c&H00CB8A27}从今往后
